headline: Starbucks' CEO Believes the Company Is on the Right Track. Is the Stock a No-Brainer Buy?
summary: Starbucks generated modest, single-digit growth last quarter.  CEO Brian Niccol is bullish on the company's future and sees a lot of potential for further improvement.  Starbucks (NASDAQ: SBUX) has been undergoing changes over the past several months in an effort to turn around its business and get back to growth.
